reviews.review_text: Grateful Dead Live at Silva Hall at the Hult Center on 1984-05-08 Love it Thank you Grateful Dead Tshirt [url="http://gratefuldeadtshirt.eshopguide.net/"]Grateful Dead Tshirt[/url]

No left turn unstoned.. Nice sound here..This is a beautiful small venue and a perfect place to see the Dead like the Berkeley Community Theater..your also in PRANKSTER territory..I'm a true believer in the venue,the crowd and the timing..when all these merge with the universe, things will turn out all right!! Not the Dead's A game but a solid show..so please>GIVE IT A WHIRL>Forever Grateful>Forever Dead!!!!!

Track order Track #4 is labeled wrong and should be Minglewood Blues.  Track #9, the second Looks like Rain, is correct and so are the rest of the tracks from there on.  Music is clear, nice Wharf Rat and Other One.  No complaints.
